{"tid":1575584,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[反骨無情]夏薩特：西班牙球迷才是真的球迷。在車路士輸波只會失望，而在皇馬則是災難。","createTime":"2019-09-17T01:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T02:21:47.000Z","uid":103207,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"95ca5df774336a1f164dcf206473d0ae87a92015","tid":1575584,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:54:32.000Z","msg":"夏薩特:在車路士輸波只會失望 而在皇馬則是災難<br />\n<br />\n  在上週同利雲特的比賽中，夏薩特上演了自己在皇馬正式比賽中的首戰，本週周中他也將迎來為皇馬出戰的首場歐冠盃比賽，賽前他接受了歐洲足協的採訪，<span style=\"color: red;\">談到了在車路士和皇馬踢球的不同</span>。<br />\n<br />\n  夏薩特表示：「<span style=\"color: red;\">在車路士輸波時，我們會很失望，就像球迷一樣，但我從來不會覺得這是一場災難，但在西班牙情況就不同了。我認為這裡的球迷才是真的球迷，足球對他們來說就是一切，他們需要球員們付出一切，而在英格蘭則沒有這麼多球迷。</span>當然了，那裡的人們也都非常喜歡足球，年青人、成年人還有青少年都對足球非常感興趣，<span style=\"color: red;\">但他們對球隊並不那麼狂熱。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n  對於皇馬教練施丹，夏薩特評價說：「我們在一切工作了超過一個月了，我感到非常開心，我覺得自己像個小孩子，這不僅是因為他，還因為其他球員。我每天都在學習，我正在漸漸瞭解他們。和教練一起工作非常棒，當你和他們交談時，你可以感覺到自己是一名真正的球員，我只需要向他學習。」<br />\n<br />\n  作為皇馬隊史最貴簽約，不少球迷都對他抱有非常高的期待，對此夏薩特表示：「這是非常特別的，<span style=\"color: red;\">當我到達這裡時，立刻能感覺到那種家的感覺。</span>我真的無法描述這種感覺，那非常令人興奮，我只想用我的腳去證明自己。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61293f04a0fd38441f71639fbffadbe1f885bba","tid":1575584,"uid":29080,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LSmmFPn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSmmFPn.gif&h=ea4a3a32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edf1541c00ed3fb8bcb17b7036f3578a7603a843","tid":1575584,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:04:49.000Z","msg":"25狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814f4da84b1e24a9aebabff8671972b901e5a15e","tid":1575584,"uid":6703,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時踢得差成班皇馬fans實噓死你，果陣夠朗都比人噓"},{"pid":"71dda23d406b9c293f6d5094723510157d06d81f","tid":1575584,"uid":103207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"edf1541c00ed3fb8bcb17b7036f3578a7603a843","tid":1575584,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:04:49.000Z","msg":"25狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:09:41.000Z","msg":"原來係賤骨頭唔可以對佢太好,要屌7佢先有家既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87873a5cee9bda3f821def4732d76d61d18afdb","tid":1575584,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:17:04.000Z","msg":"咁以你級數下年實畀人屌走<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25730311603ef9e588d78ee9daff100e4e4c9365","tid":1575584,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/cc/Chelsea_2_Spurs_0_Capital_One_Cup_winners_2015_%2816487934657%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fc%2Fcc%2FChelsea_2_Spurs_0_Capital_One_Cup_winners_2015_%252816487934657%2529.jpg&h=9fa49a78&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}